# StuckInTheMD project map

- **Repo:** [MrChriZ/StuckInTheMD](https://github.com/MrChriZ/StuckInTheMD) — C++20 Markdown editor, OS webview (not Electron).
- **Namespace / binary:** `stuckinthemd`, `stuckinthemd.exe`
- **Version:** single source in `CMakeLists.txt` → `project(StuckInTheMD VERSION …)` (title bar, installer name).

| Area | Path |
|------|------|
| App entry + webview bindings | `src/app/stuck_app.cpp`, `include/stuckinthemd/stuck_app.hpp` |
| Document / save / external file watch | `src/core/app_controller.cpp` |
| UI (embedded at configure time) | `assets/ui.html` → `build/generated/ui_embedded.cpp` |
| Tests | `tests/`, target `stuckinthemd_tests` |
| Third-party (bootstrap, do not commit clones) | `scripts/bootstrap-third-party.sh`, `third_party/` |
| CI workflows | `.github/workflows/ci.yml`, `reusable-tests.yml`, `release.yml` |
| Release notes | `RELEASE_NOTES.md` → `scripts/generate-release-notes.*` → `dist/release-notes-v*.md` |

Do not commit `build/`, `dist/`, or bootstrapped `third_party/{md4c,webview,doctest}/` trees.
